      Constructs a new Pet with specified details.
      Parameters:
      id - the pet ID
      name - the name of the pet
      age - the age of the pet
      species - the species of the pet
      breed - the breed of the pet
      healthStatus - the health status of the pet
      adopted - whether the pet is adopted
      fostered - whether the pet is fostered
      location - the location of the pet
      description - the description of the pet
      user - the user associated with the pet
      version - the version of the entity
      imageName - the name of the pet's image
